  Watch: A man jumped into a swimming pool in Pinetown to save a child from a car that had crashed into the pool. Video: Blue Security. 
 


"He jumped into the swimming pool and pulled out a two-year-old boy who had been travelling in the vehicle with his mother and a relative. 
"Redline Response paramedics responded to the scene of the accident to assist the victims, which fortunately survived the crash without sustaining any injuries," he said. 

Mathios said police were on scene. 
